{
  "stem": "26142.10",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were afraid that he recognized my brother's voice, but we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyway, he-- he was the one, actually, that was lighting the cigarette before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got-- we got all-- all scared because he saw people at night going around there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we followed the way, the directions the way he told us, but the two brothers we lost, and we couldn't find them anymore.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we started going a little further, and then-- my father owned a piece of land on that mountain, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I even remembered at one time that he came and he showed me the border of this-- this-- where that piece of land-- where it borders.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I recognized already myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We new where we are.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was a relief.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But when looking down, we knew that our house is across the street from the Hebrew day school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when we left, we knew that the command, the Hungarian command, is in the school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were-- we decided we will not go to our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Instead, we knew that on the left side at the end of this mountain, which is [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Lapszanka. ?] And that-- on that place, there is one of the 18 Jews that were left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The older one, his name was Neuman, Dudie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We will, instead, go and see if he is there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we won't go to our own house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I started telling the story-- when they surrounded the 135 families, about 800 Jews in Torun, they left 17 or 18 people-- they left in Torun.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not-- they did not deport them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Among them, among the 17 or 18, was my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
